column2: SELECT STR(z,#,#) z, ra, dec&##;  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  s.specobjid, s.specClass, s.z,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM SpecObj&##;  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE specClass=# AND dec BETWEEN # AND # AND ra BETWEEN # AND # AND z BETWEEN # AND #  p.u BETWEEN # AND #  AND g BETWEEN # AND #
